						I didn't just read feature lists. I built actual sites. Tried to export them. Launched them. Tracked them.
					</p>
					<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-white/70 mb-10">
						127 hours across 4 phases. Every failure documented. Every lock-in tactic exposed.
					</p>

					<div class="space-y-5">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F5521A]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 border border-[#F5521A]/30">
								<div class="text-xl font-black text-[#F5521A]">1</div>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-black mb-1 text-white">Generation: 8 hours</h3>
								<p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Generated 47 sites across 27+ builders. Framer had the best quality. Durable was fastest but roughest.</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F5521A]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 border border-[#F5521A]/30">
								<div class="text-xl font-black text-[#F5521A]">2</div>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-black mb-1 text-white">Customization: 34 hours</h3>
								<p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Took 3 sites from each builder and tried to make them production-ready. Hit different walls every time.</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F5521A]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 border border-[#F5521A]/30">
								<div class="text-xl font-black text-[#F5521A]">3</div>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-black mb-1 text-white">Export testing: 18 hours</h3>
								<p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Tried to export from every builder. Most "export" buttons are intentionally broken or generate garbage code.</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F5521A]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 border border-[#F5521A]/30">
								<div class="text-xl font-black text-[#F5521A]">4</div>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-black mb-1 text-white">Real launch: 67 hours</h3>
								<p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Actually launched 4 sites and tracked them for 60 days. Only 2 are still running.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<p class="text-sm text-white/50 mt-8">
						<em>Full methodology <a href="/methodology" class="text-[#F5521A] hover:underline">here</a>. Yes, I earn affiliate commissions. That doesn't change the scores.</em>
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="relative">
					<div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-8 relative overflow-hidden">
						<div class="space-y-6">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-4 pb-6 border-b border-white/10">
								<div class="text-5xl font-black text-[#F5521A]">127</div>
								<div class="text-white/80 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">hours tested</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-4 pb-6 border-b border-white/10">
								<div class="text-5xl font-black text-white">23</div>
								<div class="text-white/80 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">sites built</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-4 pb-6 border-b border-white/10">
								<div class="text-5xl font-black text-white">4</div>
								<div class="text-white/80 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">still running</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
								<div class="text-5xl font-black text-[#F5521A]">27+</div>
								<div class="text-white/80 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">builders tested</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- GUIDES - Simple link list but styled -->
	<section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-7xl">
			<div class="text-center mb-10">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">Guides</h2>
				<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">Everything I learned from 127 hours of testing</p>
			</div>

			<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-3">
				<a href="/guides/how-to-choose" class="group flex items-center justify-between p-5 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 border-[3px] border-gray-200 hover:border-[#F5521A]/50 transition-all duration-200">
					<span class="font-black text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] transition-colors">How to choose an AI website builder</span>
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
					</svg>
